Bundle/KohaSupport version 0.01
===============================

This bundle will assist in the installation of the support modules 
that are required for the Koha Open Source library System 
(see http://www.koha.org).

In addition to the modules that this bundle will install, it is 
recommended that you also install the 'yaz' client
(see http://http://www.indexdata.dk/yaz/), and once that is installed 
you can install Net::Z3950

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

GETTING HELP

The official Koha web site is at http://www.koha.org/.  There
you'll find documentation, news, etc.

The FAQ can be found at http://www.koha.org/faq/.

Several mailing lists exist for Koha users and developers. Full
information can be found at http://www.koha.org/mailing/
